    <!-- PAGE 4: NEGOTIATION PLAYBOOK -->
    <div class="page">
        <div class="page-header">
            <span class="brand">Negotiation Brief</span>
            <span class="page-num">04 / 05</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-body" style="margin-top: 0;">
            <h2 class="section-title">Creator Negotiation Playbook</h2>
            <p class="intro-text">
                Use this playbook to protect your margins and negotiate effectively with <strong>{{brandName}}</strong>. Having pre-calculated floors and up-sell multipliers ensures you never underprice your worth.
            </p>
            
            <div class="neg-block floor">
                <div class="neg-block-label">Your absolute floor price (Walk-Away Rate)</div>
                <div class="neg-block-value" style="color: #b71c1c;">₹{{floorPrice}} INR</div>
                <p class="neg-block-desc">
                    This is 70% of your recommended valuation. Do not accept anything below this for the standard deliverables unless the brand reduces usage rights, length of integration, or exclusivity duration.
                </p>
                <div class="neg-script">
                    <strong>Script:</strong> "We would love to collaborate with {{brandName}}, but to maintain our production quality and audience alignment, we cannot go below ₹{{floorPrice}} for this specific integration format."
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="neg-block counter">
                <div class="neg-block-label">Recommended Opening Offer</div>
                <div class="neg-block-value" style="color: #0d47a1; font-size: 24px;">₹{{recommendedFee}} INR</div>
                <p class="neg-block-desc">
                    Start discussions at your full calibrated value. This anchors the conversation at a premium, data-justified point, leaving room to compromise down to your target.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="neg-block extras">
                <div class="neg-block-label">Up-Sell & Licensing Add-Ons</div>
                <p class="neg-block-desc">
                    Never give away extras for free. If the sponsor requests exclusivity or usage licensing, charge these standard industry multipliers:
                </p>
                <ul class="neg-list">
                    <li><strong>Product Exclusivity (30 Days):</strong> Add <strong>₹{{exclusivityFee}} INR</strong> (+125% of base rate) to block competitors.</li>
                    <li><strong>Paid Usage Rights (30 Days):</strong> Add <strong>₹{{usageRightsFee}} INR</strong> (+20% of base rate) for running your content as ads.</li>
                    <li><strong>Link in Bio Extension:</strong> Charge a flat weekly renewal fee to keep their tracking link active.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="neg-block redflags">
                <div class="neg-block-label">Negotiation Red Flags & Warnings</div>
                <ul class="neg-list red">
                    <li><strong>Affiliate-Only Models:</strong> Reject "pure affiliate" offers unless there is a guaranteed base fee covering production time.</li>
                    <li><strong>Uncapped Usage Rights:</strong> Never sign over perpetual/unlimited advertising rights without recurring licensing payments.</li>
                    <li><strong>Vague Deliverables:</strong> Ensure exact integration lengths, script approvals, and payment timelines are written into the contract.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="page-footer">
            <span>Confidential Negotiation Brief</span>
            <span>Prepared for {{creatorName}}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

